ent-SunriseClericalErrorDeclarator = clerical error declarator
    .desc = A single-use device capable of erasing part of the station records with one decisive press. Do not ask how, we have connections.

ent-SunriseBreakerFlipDeclarator = APC outage declarator
    .desc = A single-use device that disrupts the station by randomly switching APCs. The APCs will need to be switched back manually.

ent-SunrisePowerGridCheckDeclarator = power grid declarator
    .desc = A single-use device that forcibly starts a station power grid check, temporarily cutting power across the entire station.

ent-SunriseMeteorDustDeclarator = meteor declarator
    .desc = A single-use device that signals Syndicate satellites to nudge a small portion of meteorites in the sector. Activation will cause a meteor swarm around the station.

